<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Instanceof on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/instanceof/</link><description>Recent content in Instanceof on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/instanceof/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Groovy ClassCastException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/groovy/groovy-casterror-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/groovy/groovy-casterror-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when Groovy tries to cast an object to a type it is not. This happens with explicit casts and when Groovy&amp;rsquo;s dynamic typing resolves to wrong types.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explicit cast with &lt;code&gt;as&lt;/code&gt; to wrong type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Returning wrong type from method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collection type mismatches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Groovy auto-boxing issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Java interop type mismatches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Unsafe cast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException or NumberFormatException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Check type before casting
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; Number&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Casting list element
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;three&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; nums &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; List&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException on &amp;#34;three&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Filter before casting
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;three&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; nums &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;findAll&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; it &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; Integer &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; List&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Wrong return type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getData&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Returns String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; getData&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use safe conversion
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; getData&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()?.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;isNumber&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; getData&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe casting with null check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeAsType&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; type&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; value&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;asType&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;type&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Exception e&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: instanceof check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; String&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;String: ${value}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; Number&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Number: ${value}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Unknown type: ${value.class}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Groovy type coercion
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeInt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Integer
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Exception e&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;groovy-missingmethod&lt;/a&gt; — missing method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/groovy/groovy-nullpointererror/"&gt;groovy-nullpointererror&lt;/a&gt; — null pointer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/groovy/groovy-stringindex/"&gt;groovy-stringindex&lt;/a&gt; — string index&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Java ClassCastException: Cannot Be Cast To Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/classcast-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/classcast-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="classcastexception-cannot-be-cast-to"&gt;ClassCastException: Cannot Be Cast To&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you attempt to cast an object to a type it is not an instance of at runtime. Despite Java&amp;rsquo;s compile-time type checking, casts on &lt;code&gt;Object&lt;/code&gt; references, raw collections, and generic type erasure can produce invalid casts that only fail at runtime.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java enforces type safety at compile time, but some casts bypass the compiler and are validated at runtime. When the actual object type doesn&amp;rsquo;t match the target type, the JVM throws &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Scala ClassCastException Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/scala-classcasterror-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/scala-classcasterror-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you attempt to cast an object to a type it is not. This is a runtime error that happens with &lt;code&gt;asInstanceOf&lt;/code&gt; or implicit conversions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect &lt;code&gt;asInstanceOf&lt;/code&gt; cast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type erasure in generics (e.g., &lt;code&gt;List[String]&lt;/code&gt; at runtime)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mixing incompatible types in collections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect variance in generic types&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Unsafe cast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Any&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;asInstanceOf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use pattern matching
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;s&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; i&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;i&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;toString&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Unknown type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Casting generic list (type erasure)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Any&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; strings&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;asInstanceOf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Compiles but fails!
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use collect or map
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; strings&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;collect &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Unsafe head on typed list
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; firstElement&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;list&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;head&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;asInstanceOf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Safe extraction
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; firstElement&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;list&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;List&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;headOption&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;collect &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; s
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe type checking with match
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; describe&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Any&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;s&amp;#34;String: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; i&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;s&amp;#34;Int: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; d&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Double&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;s&amp;#34;Double: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;s&amp;#34;Unknown: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;getClass&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Using ClassTag for generic type checks
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; scala.reflect.ClassTag
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; isType&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ClassTag&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;](&lt;/span&gt;value&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Any&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Boolean&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; implicitly&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ClassTag&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]].&lt;/span&gt;runtimeClass&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;isInstance&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;value&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Safe downcast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;implicit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;SafeCast&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; value&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Any&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;AnyVal&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; safeCast&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; t&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Some&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;t&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/scala-matcherror/"&gt;scala-matcherror&lt;/a&gt; — pattern match failed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;scala-nullpointer&lt;/a&gt; — null pointer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;scala-type-mismatch&lt;/a&gt; — type mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Java ClassCastException — Type Casting Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/classcastexception/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/classcastexception/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="classcastexception--type-casting-fix"&gt;ClassCastException — Type Casting Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you attempt to cast an object to a type that it is not an instance of. This is one of the most common runtime exceptions in Java, especially when working with collections, generics, and reflection.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java&amp;rsquo;s type system enforces casting rules at runtime. When you explicitly cast an object and the actual runtime type doesn&amp;rsquo;t match, the JVM throws a &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt;. Common variants:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>